headline: 3 Reasons to Sell FAST and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Over the past six months, Fastenal has been a great trade. While the S&P 500 was flat, the stock price has climbed by 9.1% to $77.12 per share. This run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
